      <section name='scarab'>

         <para number='1' comment='toss throw drop scarab'>
         As it hits the ground the scarab comes to life skittering off  before you have a chance to retrieve it.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='steal from merchant'>
         You wait until the merchant is helping another customer and hastily pocket one of the scarab beatles from the basket. Moments later you feel something wriggling in your nano-chameleon outfit. You look down to see the scarab crawling up your arm (or equivalent). You try to shake it off but it bites through your suit. Finally you manage to shake it loose. As it hits the ground it skitters back over to and climbs back up into the basket.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='BUY scarab'>
         It takes a little while but you finally catch the attention of the merchant and express interest in purchasing one of the scarab beetles. After some haggling you seal the deal for the princely sum of 13ig. You examine a couple of the beatles before selecting one and pocketing it. The merchant smiles broadly and says "You are welcome to come back any time."
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='insert use scarab w lockbook'>
         You place the scarab in the depression of the book and it seems like a perfect fit. You twist it slowly until you hear a clicking sound. Suddenly the bands that held the book closed pop open unlocking the book. You sit down to study the pages.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='insert use scarab w unlockebook'>
         The book is already unlocked!
         </para>

